-seek-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link sybase_fetch_field()} - Get field information from a result</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.sybase.php">Sybase 函数</a></div></div>
